ns>我都不愛，我不會獻給其他人(因為已獻)。<br />\n<br />\n2. 日後不管是<ins>誰</ins>都不及他愛我，只有他值得我獻出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事情好明白了，佢最愛的是他而不是你，因為在她獻出第一次給他的時候，他已預計你的出現而決定獻給他。"},{"pid":"2d9234592ae25104c44ec44ab7314e4441341cb5","tid":2329894,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"識到個令我更上心既人<br />\n希望真係放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0017293a4a773d8336122534eab7f80fb583a13","tid":2329894,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d9234592ae25104c44ec44ab7314e4441341cb5","tid":2329894,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"識到個令我更上心既人<br />\n希望真係放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"已經看透咗<br />\n所謂放低放唔低只係talk shit<br />\n因為冇野係真係會放得低<br />\n唯一可以做就係搵個第二個分心<br />\n用更多嘅開心去取代傷心<br />\n<br />\n希望你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02eb9c9061b1cff44a6052e265678a414aec13d9","tid":2329894,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:50:47.000Z","msg":"下個聖誕做俾人un 嗰個，ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fadee9c38f0910bccc52712a0f188738bc7008","tid":2329894,"uid":115162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ffbb6da68c28ffb064cfb49a794a484528ab6f","tid":2329894,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02eb9c9061b1cff44a6052e265678a414aec13d9","tid":2329894,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:50:47.000Z","msg":"下個聖誕做俾人un 嗰個，ok?<img src=\"/assets